  "title": "M&E Coordinator / Engineer",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Visit www.ourrecruiters.com</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h2>M&amp;E Coordinator/Engineer</h2>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong></li>\n  <li>Ensure smooth progress and timely delivery and completion of projects by the site teams and contractors at all times.</li>\n  <li>Identify problems and recommend areas for improvement.</li>\n  <li>Assist in tendering for new consultancy projects.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate closely with in-house QS team and facilities team.</li>\n  <li>Any other related duties as assigned from time to time.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>QUALIFICATION</strong></li>\n  <li>Diploma in Engineering</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years working experience in M&amp;E and fit-out works.</li>\n  <li>Candidate must hardworking and able to work independently and under pressure.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Visit www.ourrecruiters.com</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
